# HUD::CLEAR_GPS_FLAGS

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Clears the GPS flags. Only the script that originally called SET_GPS_FLAGS can clear them.

Doesn't seem like the flags are actually read by the game at all.
